00:18:46,200 --> 00:18:49,350
Women around Qin Zhan are countless.

307
00:18:49,750 --> 00:18:51,440
You're curious about every one of them.

308
00:18:51,440 --> 00:18:52,750
Aren't you tired?

309
00:18:54,590 --> 00:18:56,510
You were with Qin for so long.

310
00:18:56,700 --> 00:18:58,480
