311
00:19:01,350 --> 00:19:02,200
Darn it.

312
00:19:02,960 --> 00:19:04,240
Why is Jiang Dong here?

313
00:19:05,000 --> 00:19:06,000
Who is Jiang Dong?

314
00:19:07,480 --> 00:19:08,830
He's that pretty boy inside.

315
00:19:09,720 --> 00:19:10,560
I say.

316
00:19:12,070 --> 00:19:14,640
He's the man only second
to Qin in Shencheng

317
00:19:14,880 --> 00:19:17,160
