328
00:19:41,960 --> 00:19:43,400
He's not here with good intentions.

329
00:19:45,160 --> 00:19:46,590
Play it by ear.

330
00:19:54,880 --> 00:19:56,590
Sorry, we're late.

331
00:20:07,160 --> 00:20:08,270
No, we're early.

332
00:20:09,110 --> 00:20:10,720
Miss Min, nice to meet you.

333
00:20:11,400 --> 00:20:12,240
I'm Jiang Dong.

334
00:20:14,860 --> 00:20:16,460
=Grab Your Love=

